			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="An AD that triggers when players interact with a deactivated soul pillar.&#xD;&#xA;There are four different pillars in Foyer room, each one should have different description of what should happen with the souls inside. &#xD;&#xA;The idea of AD to hint on what's happening to the souls that Raphael collects.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;If players didn't succeed on a preceeding skillcheck, they don't learn anything about the souls." />
